{"tid":2349171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【戰略超前部署】澳洲議員：澳洲需準備與中國開戰","createTime":"2021-01-01T10:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T04:04:25.000Z","uid":124021,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf869a242b5311fc06eec56ea79f01cb05a8c825","tid":2349171,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"澳洲近來在牛肉與葡萄酒貿易、阿富汗爭議事件與中國關係急速惡化。澳洲參議員、前陸軍少將莫蘭（Jim Molan）<span class=\"red\">直言，澳中直接開戰可能性比想像中高，澳洲政府需要「立即準備最壞情況」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3n1dR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3n1dR2.jpg&h=9518e956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫蘭29日在澳洲7News電視台節目上表示，他<span class=\"red\">擔心澳洲與中國的貿易戰，很快就會升級為軍事衝突。</span>他強調，澳洲與中國開戰的實際機會，要比「目前所意識到的高得多」，澳洲政府需要「立即準備最壞情況」。<br />\n<br />\n莫蘭稱，<span class=\"pink\">中國已經為戰爭準備很長一段時間，最近1週每天威脅台灣，還侵入日本領空，他們對抗任何國際規則與法律，已經竊取南海，挑起對所有鄰國的戰鬥，</span>中國有非凡軍事實力，「不只是火箭與戰機，還有全方位能力來辦成一些事。」<br />\n<br />\n他預言，中國與美國會在未來3至10年內爆發戰爭，稱「美國與中國戰爭不只是可能，是比多數人願意承認的更可能。<span class=\"red\">澳洲不是主要玩家，但我們必須準備，因為我們可能遭受附帶傷害。」</span><br />\n<br />\n莫蘭表示，自己並非認為戰爭無可避免，只是認為澳洲當前最好的辦法是制訂一套防範中國的國防戰略。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3396582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3396582&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=bc1c4952\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3396582&h=66f95e9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3396582</a>"},{"pid":"f4c9ac526712da207fe90942d753078acbb8cd6d","tid":2349171,"uid":124021,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZmUfjSg2UWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZmUfjSg2UWk&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=9b0ed5e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZmUfjSg2UWk</a><br />\n原7news 節目"},{"pid":"68592f8d61b2632045e8e165ceab10226c78d744","tid":2349171,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"Next decade係指2021年開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a42f142eb8a8af84da7413b0c53752ee1b824b","tid":2349171,"uid":124021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"未來十年"},{"pid":"13e1d8864a30df6a88bf150d6c4b83f1ea9984ef","tid":2349171,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"喜歡打仔的個位老細，佢旗下的媒體真係與別不同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DS8ckHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDS8ckHw.png&h=f5bde941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28fa66830a1fa049bc530c49a2f4469a3e2c23d0","tid":2349171,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13e1d8864a30df6a88bf150d6c4b83f1ea9984ef","tid":2349171,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"喜歡打仔的個位老細，佢旗下的媒體真係與別不同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DS8ckHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDS8ckHw.png&h=f5bde941&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"大外宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83c3cbc4701d4768aea76aa12a5901be426ad61","tid":2349171,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"中國就係最鐘意係人唔留意時佔人地方之後嚇你人地唔敢開戰"},{"pid":"5055d152a45ddb0e07430af60cf1c86ad0072c49","tid":2349171,"uid":266342,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"請核爆支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c441778b12624ffbad6792522b27